    <p>Up to 100 peo­ple, in­clud­ing the wed­ding cou­ple, are al­lowed at wed­ding re­cep­tions, up from the pre­vi­ous cap of 50.</p>
    <p>All re­li­gious or­gan­i­sa­tions can con­duct ser­vices for up to</p>
    <p>100 peo­ple, with safe dis­tanc­ing and safe man­age­ment mea­sures in place.</p>
    <p>Live mu­sic dur­ing wor­ship ser­vices can re­sume at 16 re­li­gious or­gan­i­sa­tions.</p>
    <p>Re­li­gious or­gan­i­sa­tions that wish to par­tic­i­pate in the pi­lot to in­crease crowd lim­its to</p>
    <p>250 can ap­ply to do so, pro­vided they have first safely and steadily con­ducted wor­ship ser­vices for 100 peo­ple.</p>


